Mỗi field trong `pipeline_features` có mục đích:
- `phase_plan` + `validate_sub_keys`: bật/tắt Step A1 + A2
- `research_blueprint`: cho phép New Content mode  
- `split_threshold: [3, 6]`: 1-3=1ch, 4-6=2ch, 7+=3ch (configurable per niche)
- `always_include_keys`: fields gửi cho MỌI chapter (thay hardcode `core_identity`/`personal_profile`)
- `excerpt_fields`: fields dùng cho validate sub-key excerpt (thay hardcode `life_phases`)

